groups.title: SIGABA A: INDZABA
groups.instructions: Bhala indzaba NGASINYE saletihloko letingentasi ibe ngemagama la-190 kuya kula-240.

questions.text: Sitfombe semculu we-ID lebekwe etafuleni (Identity Document).
questions.context: Khetsa SINYE sitfombe kuleti letilandzelako bese ubhala ngaso indzaba. Bhala inombolo yembuto (1.6, 1.7 NOBE 1.8). Nika indzaba yakho sihloko lesifanele. CAPHELA: Akube nekubumbana kwesihloko nalesitfombe losikhetsile.

groups.title: SIGABA B: EMATHEKSTHI EMIBHALOMBIKO LEMIDZE
groups.instructions: Khetsa KUNYE kulokulandzelako ubhale ngako ngemagama la-80 kuya kula-100.

questions.text: INCWADZI YEBUHLOBO. Utfukutselise umnakenu ngekucoca indzaba latse ungayicoceli muntfu. Bhala incwadzi ucolise ngalesento losentile.
INCWADZI YEMTSETFO. Bhalela umphatsisikolo incwadzi ucele kuyosebenta njengelivolontiya emabangeni laphasi kulesikolo sakhe.

UMBIKO. Uyincenye yelitsimba lelikhetfwe beLitiko LeteNhlalakahle kutsi lente luphenyo ngetimbangela letenta lusha lusebentise tidzakamiva ngalokwecile endzaweni yangakini. Bhala umbiko lotowetfulela leLitiko.
INKHULUMO LEHLELEKILE. Ucelwe kutsi uyoba sikhulumi selusuku emcimbini lohlelwe LiTiko leTekulondvolota Emagugu Esive. Bhala inkhulumo lotayetfula ngalolosuku.

groups.title: SIGABA C: EMATHEKSTHI EMIBHALOMBIKO LEMIFISHA
groups.instructions: Khetsa KUNYE kulokulandzelako ubhale ngako ngemagama la-60 kuya kula-80.

questions.text: IPHOSTA. Uhlele umcimbi wekufundzisa bomake ngekutivulela emabhizinisi emsebenti wetandla. Bhala iphosta watise ummango wangakini ngalomcimbi.
UMBIKO LOMFISHA/WHATSAPP. Wente sivumelwano nemngani wakho sekuyobukela emafilimu edolobheni, sekunesimo lesikuvimbela kutsi ungasahambi. Bhala umbiko lomfisha umatise ngalesimo.
TICONDZISO. Bhala ticondziso longatilandzela kuvikela kulahlekelwa tinwele lesekuvamile kulamalanga.
